headline: 2026’s Biggest AI Trends: The Memory Explosion | MU Stock, SNDK Stock, SK Hynix, CAMT Stock

Over the course of 12 videos, the two will share their thoughts on everything from the memory explosion to software stocks to robotics. In this video we'll discuss why memory stocks like SanDisk (Nasdaq: SNDK), Micron (Nasdaq: MU), and SK Hynix took off in 2025 and why their stocks are continuing to run in 2026. We'll also discuss some strategies for investing in the trend in 2026 such as buying semiconductor equipment companies in the space like Camtek (Nasdaq: CAMT).
